Html:
Referring to DataGrid.Xaml, DataGridRowHeader's Width is set to a certain value &quot;16&quot;:<br />
<pre><code>&lt;Style x:Key=&quot;{x:Type DataGridRowHeader}&quot; TargetType=&quot;{x:Type DataGridRowHeader}&quot;&gt;
    &lt;Setter Property=&quot;Background&quot; Value=&quot;{DynamicResource DataGridHeaderBackground}&quot; /&gt;
    &lt;Setter Property=&quot;Foreground&quot; Value=&quot;{DynamicResource DataGridHeaderForeground}&quot; /&gt;
    &lt;Setter Property=&quot;BorderBrush&quot; Value=&quot;{DynamicResource DataGridGridLines}&quot; /&gt;
    &lt;Setter Property=&quot;BorderThickness&quot; Value=&quot;0,0,0,1&quot; /&gt;
    &lt;Setter Property=&quot;Width&quot; Value=&quot;16&quot;/&gt;
</code></pre>

I think Value &quot;Auto&quot; may be more common for different usages.<br />
